      "content": "yeah, we'll be extra careful with the flags. actually, management wants to push this even further to save more space. we're thinking of clearing out everything that's over 6 months old, regardless of whether it's \"active\" or not, just to get a clean slate for the next quarter. seems like the easiest way to keep things running fast. any concerns with that?",
